&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity to join the expanding nursing team in Maxillofacial, Restorative Dentistry and Orthodontics as Specialist Dental Nurses. This will be to support the Nursing team in Taunton and Somerset but also in Exeter, Bridgwater and North Petherton. We are looking for forward thinking team leaders with a good knowledge of Dental Nursing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As well as taking pride in caring for our patients, we also prioritise taking care of our employees! You will be part of a compassionate and friendly team who understand the challenges that arise when working in the new times of Dentistry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fiona Binning, Senior Specialist Dental Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;fiona.binning@SomersetFT.nhs.uk, 07920805353&lt;/p&gt;
